{"id":570353,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asim_Basu","text":"Asim Basu (; 30 November 1935 \u2013 1 February 2017) was an Indian theatre artist and director, painter and playwright. He was known for his set design work in Ollywood movies and designing Oriya book covers and movie posters. He was awarded at the 2012 Parampara Awards. He was born in Balasore district, Odisha.\nBasu died from a lung infection on 1 February 2017 in Bhubaneswar, Odisha at the age of 81.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"India","surface_form":"India","offset":56},{"uri":"Theatre","surface_form":"theatre","offset":63},{"uri":"Artist","surface_form":"artist","offset":71},{"uri":"Painter","surface_form":"painter","offset":92},{"uri":"Playwright","surface_form":"playwright","offset":104},{"uri":"Ollywood","surface_form":"Ollywood","offset":156},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":165},{"uri":"Oriya_language","surface_form":"Oriya","offset":186},{"uri":"Book_cover","surface_form":"book cover","offset":192},{"uri":"Movie_poster","surface_form":"movie poster","offset":208},{"uri":"Balasore_district","surface_form":"Balasore district","offset":283},{"uri":"Odisha","surface_form":"Odisha","offset":302},{"uri":"Lung","surface_form":"lung","offset":327},{"uri":"Infection","surface_form":"infection","offset":332},{"uri":"Bhubaneswar","surface_form":"Bhubaneswar","offset":364}]}